# CatFeeder feeding schedule.
#
# Install with:   crontab crontab.example      (replaces your crontab)
# or paste the line below into:   crontab -e
#
# Edit before installing:
#   - use an absolute path to the `dispense` script
#   - set your feeder's IP address
#   - set -d to your dialed-in food-flow duration in milliseconds
#
# Output is appended to a log so you can confirm each run reported OK.
#
# Field order:  minute hour day-of-month month day-of-week  command

# Feed the cats at 8:00 am and 8:00 pm every day.
0 8,20 * * *  /path/to/dispense 10.1.1.143 -d 1790 >> /var/log/catfeeder.log 2>&1
